==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hangdog
<hw>Hang"dog`</hw> <pr>(-d⟦ocr⟧g`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A base,
degraded person; a sneak; a gallows bird.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hangdog</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Hangdog
<hw>Hang"dog`</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Low; sneaking; ashamed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The poor colonel went out of the room with a <qex>hangdog</qex>
look.</q> <rj><qau>Thackeray.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hanger</ent>⟦br⟧
